resources.string: LED ko‘rinish muqovasi uchun qo‘shimcha funksiyalarni yuklab olish va o‘rnatish. O‘z LED ikonachalaringizni yaratishingiz va ularni bildirishnoma ikonachalari sifatida o‘rnatishingiz mumkin. Ularni keyinroq yuklab olish uchun Parametrlar > Qo‘shimcha funksiyalar > Aksessuarlar > LED ko‘rinish muqovasiga o‘ting, so‘ngra Qo‘shimcha funksiyalarni yuklab olishni tanlang.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
